## Context
The efficiency-accountability bimodality is the most original finding.
Nobody has tested for bimodal community structure in climate finance
quantitatively. It sharpened after 2015 (unimodal during crystallization,
bimodal in the established field). It's PC2 not PC1 — secondary but
persistent.

This is a science-studies contribution, not a methods contribution.
Different audience from the periodization paper.

## Not yet decomposed
This is a future epic. Decompose when it becomes the next priority.
May depend on the periodization paper for temporal framing.

## Exit criteria
Paper submitted to a science-studies or STS venue. The divide is
demonstrated, not just claimed. Temporal emergence is documented.
